choose Key on the bases you want to divide the data

Choos a hashfunction and hashfunction will return the shard value. and this is example of alogthermic sharding

- Data is evenly distributed in this sharding

- if the data increases you have to add a new shard , your hashing function changes data have to be move from old shard to new shard

How to use sharding key?
- should static in nature
- we can choose combination of multiple columns as well



